This 2 story 2250 sq. ft home features a great room/open concept floor plan. 1st level open kitchen/dining/living room and half bath. 2nd level offers 3B/2B and a loft/bonus space perfect for an office/bonus room. Kitchen offers quartz counter tops, grey cabinetry. Nice size master/double vanity/soaking tub and walk in closet. Large laundry room with storage. Double car garage. Beautiful covered back porch patio with BBQ Gas Hook Up. Landscaped yard with a timed sprinkler system. Enjoy Obsidian Trails walking trails, 3 maintained parks.
